graph TB
    subgraph "Llama Stack K8s Operator"
        Controller[Operator Controller Manager<br/>Deployment]
        DistController[LlamaStackDistribution Controller<br/>Go Controller]
        KustomizeTransformer[Kustomize Transformer<br/>Internal Library]
        DistResolver[Distribution Resolver<br/>Internal Component]
        NetworkMgr[Network Policy Manager<br/>Internal Component]
        StorageProvisioner[Storage Provisioner<br/>Internal Component]

        Controller -->|reconciles| DistController
        DistController -->|uses| KustomizeTransformer
        DistController -->|uses| DistResolver
        DistController -->|uses| NetworkMgr
        DistController -->|uses| StorageProvisioner
    end

    User[User/CI] -->|creates| LlamaStackDistCR[LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>v1alpha1]
    LlamaStackDistCR -->|watched by| DistController

    subgraph "Managed Resources per CR"
        ServiceAccount[ServiceAccount]
        RoleBinding[RoleBinding]
        PVC[PersistentVolumeClaim<br/>10Gi default]
        LlamaStackDeployment[Llama Stack Server<br/>Deployment]
        Service[ClusterIP Service<br/>8321/TCP]
        NetPolicy[NetworkPolicy]

        StorageProvisioner -->|creates| PVC
        DistController -->|creates| ServiceAccount
        DistController -->|creates| RoleBinding
        DistController -->|creates| LlamaStackDeployment
        DistController -->|creates| Service
        NetworkMgr -->|creates| NetPolicy

        LlamaStackDeployment -->|mounts| PVC
        Service -->|exposes| LlamaStackDeployment
        NetPolicy -->|protects| LlamaStackDeployment
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        ContainerRegistry[Container Registry<br/>quay.io 443/TCP]
        HuggingFace[HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    Controller -->|watches & manages| K8sAPI
    LlamaStackDeployment -->|pulls images| ContainerRegistry
    LlamaStackDeployment -.->|downloads models| HuggingFace

    subgraph "Inference Providers"
        Ollama[Ollama Server<br/>11434/TCP HTTP]
        vLLM[vLLM Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP]
        TGI[TGI Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP]
    end

    LlamaStackDeployment -->|inference requests| Ollama
    LlamaStackDeployment -->|inference requests| vLLM
    LlamaStackDeployment -->|inference requests| TGI

    subgraph "Observability"
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>optional]
        MetricsProxy[kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    Prometheus -->|scrapes| MetricsProxy
    MetricsProxy -->|proxies| Controller

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px
    style DistController fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style LlamaStackDistCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style LlamaStackDeployment fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style ContainerRegistry fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style HuggingFace fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Ollama fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style vLLM fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style TGI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style Prometheus fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
